data.description: Don’t miss this opportunity to get this home under market value! New Reduced Price.Gorgeous one story with upgrades in the sought after subdivision of River Ridge.  This Crandall ISD, beautiful open home has 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home with many upgrades throughout. Upgrades include new roof, hvac in 2019, water heater, flooring, and more.The open floorplan offers plenty of room and low HOA. Perfect location for Crandall ISD beauty is ready for you to call it home! Open concept living space to the kitchen makes for the perfect home for entertaining. Large extended patio and backyard will be perfect for the next BBQ season.The Primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom, separate tub and shower and walk in closet adds a retreat type atmosphere for you.This perfect layout has secondary bedrooms located separate to give a more private environment. Large utility room with shelves for more storage.Perfect location commuting to Dallas.
